1. Install Playwright Core & Cucumber Support
This installs the library that your playwright.config.ts is trying to import.

Bash
npm install @playwright/test playwright-gherkin
2. Install Browser Binaries
Playwright needs its own versions of Chromium, Firefox, and WebKit to run.

Bash
npx playwright install
3. Install System Dependencies (If prompted)
If your Mac asks for permissions or mentions missing system libraries, run:

Bash
npx playwright install-deps

npm install @cucumber/cucumber